# https://opensource.com/article/17/11/how-use-cron-linux
#
# * * 1 * * instead of ∃¬x:end_of_month
# */3 01-03 * * 1,3,5 every 3m between 1am & 3am on mon,wed,fri
#
# minute∈{[0,60)}
# |hour∈{[0,24)}
# ||day_of_month∈{[1,31]}
